<?xml version="1.0"?>
<gpx xmlns="http://www.topografix.com/GPX/1/1" xmlns:gpxx="http://www.garmin.com/xmlschemas/GpxExtensions/v3" creator="CALTOPO" version="1.1"><metadata><name><![CDATA[Chamisa Saddleback Loop]]></name></metadata><trk><name>Chamisa Saddleback Loop</name><desc>Popularity: 2/5
Difficulty: 3/5
Dates: 4/15 - 12/1

When the snow has started falling higher up (or hasn't thawed), and you want your mountain kick, this loop is a great option. Get your big climbs in early as you run along the Saddleback trail, then a satisfying descent along Burn, followed by the enchanting, gentle(?) climb up the Winsor along Big Tesuque Creek.

Expect to see a decent number of folks on the Winsor and Chamisa portions, but Saddleback and Burn are mostly empty and are great trails for running.</desc><trkseg><trkpt lat="35.72880527187041" lon="-105.86602159790039"><ele>2387.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.72868000000001" lon="-105.86604"><ele>2387.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.72868" lon="-105.86604"><ele>2387.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.72868" lon="-105.86604"><ele>2387.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.72876" lon="-105.86601000000002"><ele>2387.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.72876" lon="-105.86601000000002"><ele>2387.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.72876" lon="-105.86601000000002"><ele>2387.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.72912" lon="-105.86597"><ele>2390.706279111095</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.72976" lon="-105.86563999999998"><ele>2395.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.73008" lon="-105.86559999999997"><ele>2397.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.7302" lon="-105.86554999999998"><ele>2397.0193672041332</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.73062" lon="-105.86529999999999"><ele>2401.002963907655</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.73098" lon="-105.86502000000002"><ele>2405.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.73161" lon="-105.86487999999997"><ele>2409.878404332325</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.73194" lon="-105.86473999999998"><ele>2412.823805416003</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.73262" lon="-105.86426"><ele>2420.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.73262" lon="-105.86426"><ele>2420.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.733" lon="-105.86392000000001"><ele>2423.078004823678</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.73344" lon="-105.86369000000002"><ele>2427.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.73359" lon="-105.86367000000001"><ele>2428.105952000711</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.73415" lon="-105.86370999999997"><ele>2434.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.73435" lon="-105.86365999999998"><ele>2435.1184000828803</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.7348" lon="-105.86333000000002"><ele>2440.2813735068776</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.7355" lon="-105.86275999999998"><ele>2452.906365745701</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="